# `PUT` `/api/{store}/pets/whiskers?path=favFood.[0]` with body `"carrot"` updates the first element in the `favFood` array only. So a `GET` request to `/api/{store}/pets/whiskers` would now show the updated `favFood`:

```json
{
    "name": "wisker",
    "favFood": [
        "carrot",
        "rabbit"
    ]
}
```

